{
  "texts": [
    "For English oral instructions, LLMs, especially IPAs like Google Assistant and Amazon Alexa, demonstrate the ability to help EFL learners overcome speaking anxiety by supporting them with encouraging conversation and immediate feedback [8,9].",
    "Besides, even though human experts are more professional and more empathetic than LLM-based applications [7], they can provide EFL learners with powerful assistance for self-studying when human experts are not affordable or available [7,9,10].",
    "For English writing instructions, researchers mainly focused on exploring the usage of ChatGPT.",
    "They proved ChatGPT's abilities to answer writing questions, provide suggestions and feedback, and detect surface mistakes [11][12][13], but whether MMLs are able to improve EFL learner's writing motivation requires further research.",
    "In general, these studies show a bright prospect of integrating LLMs into EFL education, which would enhance the efficiency and performance of traditional education.However, while the power of LLMs is proven, these articles also exhibit some similar concerns about LLMs' performances and reliability at present."
  ]
}